claim.claim-text:
The apparatus (10) of claim 1 wherein the gun is

a pistol;

semi-automatic;

a revolver;

a rifle;

a shotgun;

a paint-ball gun; or

an electronic stun gun.

The apparatus (10) of claim 5 wherein the light source has a first end (20A) and a second end (20B), and the light source adjustment apparatus (300) comprises a first elastomeric collar (312) that fits over the first end (20A) of the light source and a second elastomeric collar (314) that fits over the second end (20B) of the light source;
preferably wherein the sighting device includes: (a) a housing (200) that retains the light source and the light source adjustment apparatus (300), the housing (200) including one or more apertures (206A, 208A); and (b) a set screw (225) received in at least one of the one or more apertures (206A, 208A), wherein the light source is movable by adjusting the set screw (225); and
more preferably the housing (200) has two apertures (206A, 208A) and a set screw (225) positioned in each aperture, and the light source can be moved by adjusting either of the set screws (225).

Appareil (10) selon la revendication 1, dans lequel l'arme à feu est
un pistolet ;
un semi-automatique ;
un revolver ;
un fusil ;
un fusil de chasse ;
un fusil de paint-ball ; ou
un pistolet paralysant électronique.
